{"article_id":"IUEKHlSQYUiGOxla","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Bart Jansen and Sean Rossman and Doug Stanglin and Kevin Johnson","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"WAS","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"INGTON -","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"ikiLeaks founder Julian Assange was arrested Thursday","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"o face a U.S. charge","depth":13},{"id":5,"text":"hat he conspired to hack military computers","depth":13},{"id":6,"text":"fter Ecuador 's government ended his seven years of self-imposed exile","depth":13},{"id":7,"text":"nd expelled him from its London embassy .","depth":13},{"id":8,"text":"olice in the United Kingdom dragged Assange from the front door of the embassy Thursday morning .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"e now faces extradition to the United States .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"n an indictment","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"evealed Thursday morning ,","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":".S. authorities say","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"ssange conspired with former Army intelligence analyst Chelsea Manning to steal and publish huge troves of classified documents .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"rosecutors said","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"ssange at one point tried to help Manning crack a password","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"o access military computers","depth":15},{"id":17,"text":"here the information was stored .","depth":15},{"id":18,"text":"ver four months in 2010 , Manning downloaded hundreds of thousands of secret reports on the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan , as well as State Department cables and information about detainees in Guantanamo Bay , Cuba .","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"anning turned the records over to WikiLeaks ,","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"hich passed them to journalists","depth":15},{"id":21,"text":"nd published them on the internet .","depth":15},{"id":22,"text":"rosecutors said","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"t was one of the most extensive leaks of classified secrets in U.S. history .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"ssange is charged with conspiracy","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"o commit computer intrusion .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"he charge ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"elivered by a federal grand jury in March 2018","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"ut kept secret until Thursday ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"arries a maximum sentence of five years in prison .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"arry Pollack , a U.S. lawyer for Assange , criticized the arrest","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"nd said","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"ssange would need medical treatment","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"hat had been denied for seven years .","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"` It is bitterly disappointing that a country would allow someone","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"o whom it has extended citizenship and asylum","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"o be arrested in its embassy , ''","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"ollack said .","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"' Once his health care needs have been addressed ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"he UK courts will need to resolve what appears to be an unprecedented effort by the United States","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"eeking to extradite a foreign journalist","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"o face criminal charges","depth":16},{"id":42,"text":"or publishing truthful information . ''","depth":16},{"id":43,"text":"ndictment :","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"ulian Assange indictment :","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"ead the grand jury indictment against the WikiLeaks founder","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"ssange had sheltered in Ecuador 's embassy","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"ince seeking asylum there in 2012 .","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"ondon 's Metropolitan Police moved in","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"fter Ecuador formally withdrew its asylum for Assange , an Australian native ,","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"nd revoked his Ecuadorian citizenship .","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"lainclothes officers escorted him from the embassy Thursday .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"n a British court Thursday , Judge Michael Snow issued a guilty verdict against Assange","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"or breaching his bail conditions .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"ssange ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"ho appeared in the Westminster Magistrates ' Court","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"here his supporters packed the public gallery ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"aces a sentence of up to 12 months in prison for the conviction .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"ritish Prime Minister Theresa May said","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"ssange ' s arrest shows","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"` no one is above the law . ''","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"he arrest followed months of carefully orchestrated diplomatic maneuvering by the Ecuadorian government","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"hat had long soured on its relationship with Assange .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"n a videotaped statement , Ecuadorian president Lenin Moreno said","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"is country 's patience `` has reached its limit , ''","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"iting bizarre behavior inside the embassy and violations of the country 's demand","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"hat he stop interfering in the affairs of other governments .","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"oreno described it as a \" sovereign decision \"","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"s a result of \" repeated violations to international conventions and daily life . \"","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"ssange was taken into custody on a 2012 warrant","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"or jumping bail","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"hile facing extradition to Sweden on sexual assault allegations .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"he Swedish accusations have since been dropped ,","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"ut he was still wanted for the bail violation .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"he Justice Department said","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"t was seeking his extradition to the United States .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"hat process can be a lengthy one .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"e will be entitled to a hearing in London","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"here he can dispute the U.S. request .","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"` What he ' s going to do is to say","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"hat the extradition request is entirely political","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"nd its intention is to punish him for Wikileaks , ''","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"aid John Hardy , a London-based lawyer","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"ho specializes in extradition .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"hat could take as long as two years","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"f Assange appeals to the United Kingdom 's highest court ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"ardy said .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"he U.S. charges center on his interactions with Manning .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"rosecutors said","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"ssange encouraged her to leak classified secrets to the anti-secrecy group","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"nd tried to help her crack a password to Defense Department computers","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"hat stored classified secrets .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"hat would have allowed Manning to log on to the computer network with someone else 's username .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"he indictment said","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"nvestigators obtained messages between the two","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"n which Manning provided Assange `` part of a password '' on March 8 , 2010 .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"wo days later , Assange asked for more information about the password","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"nd indicated","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"hat he had been trying to crack the password","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"ut so far had not succeeded .","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"rosecutors said","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"ssange also encouraged Manning to look for more classified information","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"o disclose .","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"n March 7 , 2010 , Manning and Assange discussed the Guantanamo records ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"ccording to the indictment .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"anning told Assange the next day","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"hat \" after this upload , that ' s all","depth":16},{"id":107,"text":"really have got left , \"","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"he indictment said .","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"ssange replied","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"hat \" curious eyes never run dry in my experience , ''","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"he indictment said .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"eparately , Assange has been under scrutiny for years for WikiLeaks ' role","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"n publishing government secrets .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"ikiLeaks , the transparency group","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"hat he founded ,","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"as also front and center of the 2016 presidential election","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"or leaking emails","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"acked from the Democratic National Committee .","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"uring the presidential campaign , then-candidate Donald Trump repeatedly praised the organization ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"aying numerous times at rallies ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"` I love WikiLeaks . ''","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"ederal prosecutors have said","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"he emails were stolen by hackers","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"orking for Russia 's military intelligence service ,","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"hich gave them to WikiLeaks as part of an effort","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"o sway the presidential election in Trump 's favor .","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"he charges","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"evealed Thursday","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"re unrelated to that effort .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"oreno , the Ecuadorian president , said","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"ssange `` will not be extradited to a country","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"here he could suffer torture or the death penalty. ``","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"e said","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"he British government confirmed that in writing .","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"n a list of grievances , Moreno said","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"ssange had installed prohibited electronic equipment in the embassy ,","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"locked security cameras","depth":17},{"id":138,"text":"nd even `` accessed the security files of our embassy","depth":18},{"id":139,"text":"ithout permission . ''","depth":18},{"id":140,"text":"e said","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"ssange also had `` confronted and mistreated the diplomatic guards . ''","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"ritish Foreign Secretary Jeremy Hunt told reporters Thursday","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"hat the arrest shows","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"hat `` no one is above the law . '","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"`` Julian Assange is no hero , ''","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"e said .","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"unt said","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"he operation came after `` years of careful diplomacy ''","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"nd praised Moreno for his `` very courageous decision . ''","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"` It 's not so much Julian Assange being held hostage in the Ecuadorian Embassy , ''","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"unt said .","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"` It ' s actually Julian Assange holding the Ecuadorian Embassy hostage in a situation","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"hat was absolutely intolerable for them . ''","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"ssange-Ecuador :","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"cuador accuses Julian Assange of violating asylum deal in London embassy","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"cuador president","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"nough guarantees","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"or WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange to leave embassy ,","depth":16},{"id":159,"text":"eturn to UK","depth":16},{"id":160,"text":"ssange took refuge in the embassy","depth":17},{"id":161,"text":"o avoid extradition to Sweden","depth":18},{"id":162,"text":"or questioning over rape allegations .","depth":18},{"id":163,"text":"ssange , an Australian national , chose to remain in the embassy out of fear","depth":17},{"id":164,"text":"hat the United States would immediately seek his arrest and extradition over the leaking of classified documents to WikiLeaks by Manning .","depth":17},{"id":165,"text":"ikileaks said in a Thursday tweet","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"hat `` Powerful actors ,","depth":18},{"id":167,"text":"ncluding CIA ,","depth":18},{"id":168,"text":"re engaged in a sophisticated effort","depth":18},{"id":169,"text":"o dehumanize , delegitimize and imprison him . ''","depth":18},{"id":170,"text":"ssange ,","depth":17},{"id":171,"text":"ho was granted Ecuadorian citizenship last year in an apparent effort","depth":18},{"id":172,"text":"o designate him a diplomat","depth":19},{"id":173,"text":"nd allow him to go to Russia ,","depth":19},{"id":174,"text":"ued Ecuador","depth":17},{"id":175,"text":"or violating his rights as an Ecuadorian .","depth":17},{"id":176,"text":"e pressed his case in local and international tribunals on human rights grounds ,","depth":16},{"id":177,"text":"ut both ruled against him .","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"n 2011 , the leftist Ecuadorian government","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"hat initially offered asylum to Assange","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"ad been embroiled in a diplomatic row with the United States","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"nvolving a leaked U.S. diplomatic cable .","depth":17},{"id":182,"text":".S. ambassador to Ecuador Heather Hodges was expelled","depth":17},{"id":183,"text":"fter WikiLeaks leaked the document","depth":18},{"id":184,"text":"hat alleged widespread corruption within the Ecuadorian police force ,","depth":18},{"id":185,"text":"he BBC reported .","depth":16},{"id":186,"text":"ssange first got a taste","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"f tapping into unauthorized material","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"hen he became a hacker in 1987 .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"our years later he was convicted of hacking into the master terminal of Nortel , a Canadian multinational telecommunications corporation ,","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"he New Yorker reported .","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"pinion :","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"ulian Assange deserves a Medal of Freedom , not a secret indictment","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"n 2006 , Assange established WikiLeaks as a site","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"or publishing classified information","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"nd within a decade had posted more than 10 million documents","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"ften embarrassing to governments .","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"hile gaining the backing of some world figures ,","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"ncluding leaders of Brazil and Ecuador ,","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"e gained international notoriety","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"fter publishing information in 2010 ,","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"hich was leaked by a self-described whistleblower inside the U.S. Army , Bradley Manning , a transgender woman","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"ho later became known as Chelsea Manning .","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"anning spent nearly seven years in prison","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"or leaking classified and sensitive military and diplomatic documents .","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"ontributing :","depth":4},{"id":206,"text":"illiam Cummings and Deirdre Shesgreen of ; The Associated Press","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":413,"left":0,"right":412,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":412,"left":1,"right":411,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":411,"left":409,"right":410,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":409,"left":2,"right":408,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":408,"left":396,"right":407,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":396,"left":290,"right":395,"relation":"e